Second advances to Globo, it is a Brazilian woman, 35, who traveled from Shanghai, China, to Brazil. The Secretariat of Health State of Minas Gerais is now investigating the case.



The woman has already been subjected to exams, which will confirm or discard this possibility. The woman presents respiratory symptoms compatible with that acute viral respiratory disease.
